      "author_association" : "CONTRIBUTOR",
      "body" : "At least on Unix systems you can take a look at the QSettings bitcoin-qt file.\r\nThere they are stored at `~/.config/Bitcoin` (IIRC).\r\nOn Windows it is probably in `%APPDATA%\\Bitcoin`.\r\nThere is a string which says where the datadir is located",
